00:02:28,040 --> 00:02:30,670
¡Kura-san, mátelo! ¡Kura-san!

523
00:03:29,980 --> 00:03:32,780
¡Empujen!

524
00:03:34,320 --> 00:03:36,780
¡Ahí va!

525
00:03:45,370 --> 00:03:48,540
¡Muere, hipnotizador!

526
00:04:07,140 --> 00:04:08,310
¡Tamanegi!

527
00:08:22,940 --> 00:08:26,400
Mola

528
00:08:22,940 --> 00:08:26,400
Shi

529
00:08:22,940 --> 00:08:26,400
Chibukai

530
00:08:22,940 --> 00:08:26,400
Fansub!

531
00:08:22,940 --> 00:08:26,400
Cucharón de la muerte.

532
00:10:03,040 --> 00:10:06,000
¿Q-Qué está sucediendo?

533
00:10:06,000 --> 00:10:10,010
¡Algo los está cortando de repente!

534
00:10:23,060 --> 00:10:25,900
¡Muéstrate, mayordomo!

535
00:13:23,280 --> 00:13:25,490
¡Kaya-san!

536
00:15:15,890 --> 00:15:17,440
Te equivocas.

537
00:15:27,490 --> 00:15:29,410
¡Capitán!

538
00:15:50,220 --> 00:15:52,350
Mola

539
00:15:50,220 --> 00:15:52,350
Shi

540
00:15:50,220 --> 00:15:52,350
Chibukai

541
00:15:50,220 --> 00:15:52,350
Fansub!

542
00:15:50,220 --> 00:15:52,350
Estrella letal de pólvora.

543
00:15:58,100 --> 00:16:03,400
...Kane!

544
00:15:58,100 --> 00:16:03,440
Mola

545
00:15:58,100 --> 00:16:03,440
Shi

546
00:15:58,100 --> 00:16:03,440
Chibukai

547
00:15:58,100 --> 00:16:03,440
Fansub!

548
00:15:58,100 --> 00:16:03,440
Campana.

549
00:16:14,200 --> 00:16:21,080
Cuando era pequeño, extendía...

550
00:16:21,420 --> 00:16:28,050
...un mapa del tesoro en mi mente.

551
00:16:28,430 --> 00:16:35,310
Me aseguraba de que ningún
 desconocido se me adelantara...

552
00:16:35,270 --> 00:16:42,230
...en alcanzar ese lugar milagroso que buscaba.

553
00:16:45,110 --> 00:16:47,610
Mi verdadero...

554
00:16:49,860 --> 00:16:56,290
...sueño tiene que realizarse.

555
00:16:56,580 --> 00:17:03,590
Si el mundo cambiase algún día,

556
00:17:03,840 --> 00:17:10,630
llévenme con el yo que nunca supo nada...

557
00:17:10,760 --> 00:17:23,650
...y asegúrense de que los recuerdos no se esfumen.

